relevant_findings.HEENT: Sclera anicteric, moist mucous membranes, oropharynx clear
relevant_findings.neck: Supple, jugular venous pressure not elevated, no lymphadenopathy
relevant_findings.lungs: Clear to auscultation bilaterally, no wheezes, rales, or rhonchi
relevant_findings.cardiovascular: Regular rate and rhythm, normal S1 and S2, no murmurs, rubs, or gallops
relevant_findings.abdomen: Tender to palpation in RUQ, rebound tenderness present, soft, non-distended
relevant_findings.extremities: Warm, well perfused, 2+ pulses, no clubbing, cyanosis, or edema
relevant_findings.neurological: No slurred speech, no focal weakness, wide-based shuffling gait, cerebellar testing (finger to nose and Romberg) normal
